4. AGENT IDENTITY ROYALTY
   Cryptographic identities generated through the /identity/* endpoints
   or derivative identity services carry a one-time generation fee as
   defined in the marketplace pricing. Derivative identity services
   must remit 5% of identity-related revenue to Phantom Capital.

5. x402 MICROPAYMENT ROYALTY
